#: en/adminarea.xml:310
msgid "By default, the QueueView only lists tickets in queues that an agent has <emphasis>rw</emphasis> access to, i.e., the tickets the agent needs to work on. If you want to change this behaviour, you can set <link linkend=\"Ticket:Frontend::Agent::Ticket::ViewQueue:Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketQueue_ViewAllPossibleTickets\"> Ticket::Frontend::AgentTicketQueue###ViewAllPossibleTickets </link> to <emphasis>Yes</emphasis>."
