#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:495
msgid "OTRS supports different types of users. Using the link \"Customers\" (via the navigation bar or the admin area), you can manage the accounts of your customers (see Figure 5.14 below), who can can log into the system via the customer interface (customer.pl). Through this interface, your customers can create tickets and access to them. It is importan to know that a customer is needed for the ticket history in the system."
