#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:523
msgid "To create a new customer account, click on the \"Add customer\" button (see Figure 5.15 below). Some of the fields are mandatory, i.e., they have to contain values, so if you leave one of those empty, it will be marked and a message will be displayed."
